Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.94,0:00:17.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}微风轻吻着脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.25,0:00:21.37,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}用着一种怀念的温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.55,0:00:29.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹干流下的泪珠轻拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.19,0:00:40.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是谁 对未来都着着一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.47,0:00:49.07,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝着明天大步迈进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.71,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.71,0:00:58.08,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}总有一天会觉醒的 真实心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.35,0:01:04.19,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}现在就伸出双手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:14.43,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在这开始变化的世界 立刻前往探寻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.67,0:01:20.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牵系着你的手绝不再分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.48,0:01:23.53,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因为有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.58,0:01:28.31,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找寻的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三号机接近目标中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.72,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四点钟方向有敌影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.34,0:01:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉目标集团 准备发射飞弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 出力调至150%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准范围目标数28、29…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.44,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边那位 表情帅气一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.07,0:02:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好   卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.11,0:02:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0K了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.75,0:02:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第十一话  说不出口」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.19,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像刚才所示 两人为了加强彼此的默契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.56,0:02:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日夜都接受着严格的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事无所谓 快播下去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.13,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很吵耶 一直乱叫\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(那么就采访速水驾驶员)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊、来了来了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(速水是双人座机驾驶员吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有拍到了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(是的)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看在这 拍到我了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(那至今都跟芝村合作吗）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.87,0:02:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水…\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(平常的休闲是？)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.44,0:03:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙！\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(平常就是慢跑或读书)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错啦\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(最后请问一个问题)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村对你而言是怎样的存在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.05,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得…是很好的搭档…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.23,0:03:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着采访芝村 操纵工作很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 记得芝村后来是说…\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(没什么问题)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于芝村而言 速水是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很好的…工作上的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(非常感谢各位的协助)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还问怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.81,0:03:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道还有其他回答吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.82,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 望望美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说是工作上的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这个地步了 与其说顽固 倒不如是偏执呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水跟芝村最近的感觉不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会让人忍不住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 赶快交往不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要等他们自然交往也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.51,0:04:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有什么办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姊你说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.61,0:04:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.55,0:04:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是来自尚敬高中5121部队\N「突击！话题之两人」的专栏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了和平而战斗的两人 希望各位为他们加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.63,0:04:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很不满呢 善行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.87,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都写在脸上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.51,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来要决定负责的工作\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(5121部队圣诞派对)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责购物的要男女各一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁负责比较好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得女生找芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后男生找速水就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.09,0:04:54.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁赞成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.09,0:04:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.59,0:04:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.89,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么问 刚刚决定的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是工作上的搭档吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是买东西的顺序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面没买完 不准开后面的信封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.35,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你有意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人在圣诞夜去买东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像在约会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.36,0:05:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也有过美好的回忆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我前一天就很紧张呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找朋友讨论该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.78,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还烦恼要穿哪件衣服 这些过程都很有趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得没有容身之处呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快把东西买完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标从通町路前往商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如预定前往A地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知诱敌部队 目标接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进入临战态势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以顺利成功吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不都是春香无意间扯后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.35,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样再失败的话 我就生气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想问一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.76,0:06:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须请说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.99,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道 为什么我是麋鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想当圣诞老人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.93,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 我们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.84,0:06:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-圣诞快乐 现在是特惠活动喔\N-请参考看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.38,0:07:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}(热恋的二人之快速占卜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 去买下一个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是圣诞老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经撒饵了 状况进行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.79,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来须
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.29,0:07:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你命中注定的伴侣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟之内被告白的话 你们的恋情将永志不渝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运物是木制的长椅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.87,0:07:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼中已经只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30分钟之内告白 一定会成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.47,0:07:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运物是喷水池
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种乱七八糟的占卜好多呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.99,0:07:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 害得年底的气氛都怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是圣诞老人 任务结束 现在准备归队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看他们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑他们的话 他们会很可怜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没在笑他们啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快买完东西才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.64,0:08:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家都在等呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.86,0:08:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实很…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.44,0:08:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜…喜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.81,0:08:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是很爱你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是衷心地爱你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 我要走了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 美惠子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶快去买东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水厚志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.59,0:09:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丢下我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.61,0:09:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一阶段失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那个没毅力的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.24,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事就是不简单才有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你们了 快回来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.89,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到 现在将前往交班地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边 接下来麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.53,0:10:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪位可以借我电车钱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远坂 跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他不是真命天子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他分开之后的下一个才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢你了\N-谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位还记得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.56,0:10:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚敬高中5121部队的那两个人 在圣诞夜被我们抓到啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来感情很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的计划是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看电影？喝下午茶？还是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢她哪个地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 她本人是听不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.07,0:10:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说你不好意思说出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.45,0:10:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是工作上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是因为要买东西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是女方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 请站在摄影机前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这间店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.85,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在这里买外套跟长裤 而且配色要够好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确定上面是这么写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配色？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年这一系列很受欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.37,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要帮您做介绍吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.24,0:11:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是我要穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友要我帮忙买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.01,0:11:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心不要被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.48,0:11:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圣诞节的礼物吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那等到选好再通知我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞派对需要这些吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.28,0:12:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是远坂 田边严重受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由这边先行收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.55,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田边？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.79,0:12:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边都是本店的新作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这里没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.07,0:12:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村 果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.58,0:13:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派对不应该买这种高价饰品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一点就被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.06,0:13:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过芝村应该也有所警觉了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 都已经走到这一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.33,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要任凭发展就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问要找什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的话可以帮您拿出来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们应该是搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.49,0:13:57.99,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a7}你一个不经意的举止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.37,0:14:04.86,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}就让我冰冻的心得以融化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.27,0:14:12.14,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}回头所露出令我心动的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.41,0:14:19.15,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}让失去色彩的城市变得鲜艳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:25.88,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}我不知道未来会是如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:34.66,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}但我明天仍想仰望蓝天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.03,0:14:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.16,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}好想要奔跑的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是最后一个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.90,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}想这么扑到你的怀里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.04,0:14:48.41,OPED,NTP,0010,0010,0010,,{\fs18\fad(100,100)\a3}你双手接着我凝视着我 两人一起乘风而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水厚志先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.06,0:15:05.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您已经预约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.57,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮您把手提物品放在寄物柜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.09,0:15:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要点预约时所订的圣诞特制晚餐A餐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.36,0:15:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.22,0:15:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得心怦怦跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过学姊知道的地方好棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.47,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想在那种地方被告白呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有订到好位子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.37,0:15:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 要看夜景绝对没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只要吃饭不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们根本就是白费工夫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运动型的不要说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这种是要顺其自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:15:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我所选的珠宝店可是让小舞非常满意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百元商店是我的意见喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说谁曾经去那间店花大钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.89,0:16:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是去让别人花钱的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.40,0:16:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的百元商店…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这趟购物之旅很奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.91,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到会有这么一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.41,0:16:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.02,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会是芝村先开口吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今都是一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.43,0:16:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使知道不会结束 从那天起我还是独自走来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望能够尽量多杀些幻兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 那天是哪天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将其当成是在继承遗志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在对马战死的那个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这只是在逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想不到其他的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人背负一切作战 然后在心中对自己妥协
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.16,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样就行了 孤单一个人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被编到5121部队时也这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.27,0:17:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次跟你搭乘双人座机也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.64,0:17:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是忘不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了那个人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.75,0:17:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人怎么了吗？客人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白痴吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.07,0:18:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村舞 芝村舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请尽快到教职员室来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是本部的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你以双人座机驾驶员的身份 前往缺人的8312部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 是转调邀请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是邀请 不是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话可以拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何 决定权在于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.30,0:19:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于还有一些时间 你就好好考虑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}昨天的圣诞夜各位怎么过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.08,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}以下是黑川记者在街上的突击采访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.49,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}各位好 我是黑川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐厅还有开吗\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(马上就来采访这对情侣吧)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.79,0:19:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年好像开到29号\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(男朋友？不是啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(所以他不是真命天子吗)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}跟他分开之后的下一个才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}各位还记得吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.60,0:19:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}尚敬高中5121部队的那两个人 在圣诞夜被我们抓到啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}看起来感情很好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}今天的计划是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}看电影？喝下午茶？还是说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}喜欢她哪个地方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.35,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}没关系 她本人是听不到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.09,0:19:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}还是说你不好意思说出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}那么接下来就问女方啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}虽然看起来不大可靠 不过他其实蛮可爱对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}大家都叫他小呆瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}小呆瓜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}不过这也是他的魅力之一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}这个我可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}那最后再问个问题 他对你而言是怎样的存在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.89,0:20:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}是很好的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}工作上的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}是很好的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.73,0:20:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fnsimhei}速水厚志是我重要的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是忘不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了那个人对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.69,0:21:48.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}最重要的心情 总是过于接近无法传达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.67,0:22:00.48,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}擦肩而过时的悲伤 在我的内心紧紧纠结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.91,0:22:06.44,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}雨过天睛 光珠般的雨滴
